{"tid":1782638,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港能，中共不能的原因。/日本能，中國不能的原因","createTime":"2019-12-14T06:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T13:52:40.000Z","uid":7736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe341b0a7431845f85393a6c2fca1538f40529bc","tid":1782638,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"明治維新-呂理洲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6xhpWP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6xhpWP.png&h=d6c60993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">強烈建議大家睇依本書<br />\n</span><br />\n試將德川政府 替換成中共。<br />\n（因為佢地特質非常相同，<br />\n當然CCP更on9無可否認）完全沒有違和感。<br />\n<br />\n而香港同香港人特質，同日本改革派有好多相似嘅地方。<br />\n了解明治維派的心路歷程，可比大家心理準備。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7RVbyG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7RVbyG.png&h=e6c2bbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信經過幾過月，大家都知，不論中共人民，<br />\n甚至高層對現實嘅掌握度，非常之差。<br />\n（可能因為中國式政治，所謂嘅民族思緒影響，<br />\n給由上而下嘅奴隸思想，所阻礙）<br />\n依個係我哋香港人，有機會贏的其中一個關鍵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54qrieO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54qrieO.png&h=128c0c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.日本有蘭學，中國冇/<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港有深厚英國文化根底，中共冇</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6GjWFr7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6GjWFr7.png&h=ead0ae29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.中國有科舉，日本冇<br />\n（科舉是嚴重限制 學者思想的產物）/<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中共有思想控制措施，香港180年歷史冇</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWqOwyZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWqOwyZ.png&h=ec93a60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.日本有武士道，中國冇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">（說明人民學會軍事知識和技巧的重要性）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiz7M7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feiz7M7x.png&h=38b61110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.中國文化優越感 比 日本強！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中共優越感 比 香港強！（玻璃心）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOh9f05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOh9f05.png&h=cb6581b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xAfbzD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xAfbzD.png&h=952fead8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">強烈建議大家，買返本<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0dc928283dcc700809e3c58036f3647c44546512","tid":1782638,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:42:41.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b09c0c3a79782e0bca2442182034439a1cb7d29e","tid":1782638,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"中華民國都仲有啲有識之仕管住<br />\n到了共產黨就係山蕃管山蕃。文革之後更甚。"}]}